data.description: Nestled in the foothills on a 50-acre gated property, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home, complete with wrap around porch, offers the perfect blend of pasture and woods. Made for equestrians, this beautiful property features a 40x110 barn complete with a tackroom, 3 stalls (2021) and a covered outdoor arena. Enjoy new HVAC units (2023), a Generac generator (2022), and fresh well water (new pump 2021). The outdoor bar (2022), equipped with a built-in kegerator, mini fridge, and grill, is an entertainer's dream, not to mention the built in smoker! Relax in wood-fenced pastures or under your own pear trees and fig bush. Experience the perfect balance of mountain serenity and modern convenience!
